{
  "page": "Seven Speakers",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Seven Speakers</b> were seven preachers - three men and four women - selected by King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> to win over the support of the people of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> for his rule and his marriage to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> through the <a href=\"/index.php/Doctrine_of_Exceptionalism\" title=\"Doctrine of Exceptionalism\">Doctrine of Exceptionalism</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Seven_Speakers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Seven Speakers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes_from_the_Seven_Speakers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes from the Seven Speakers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Speakers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryens</a> public <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> to his sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>, the king took precautions to assure that his marriage would be accepted by his subjects. He reasoned that his marriage to Alysanne would not cause another <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a> as the marriage of his eldest brother and sister had done in <a href=\"/index.php/41_AC\" title=\"41 AC\">41&#160;AC</a>, for a number of reasons: the current <a href=\"/index.php/High_Lickspittle\" title=\"High Lickspittle\">High Septon</a> was a passive man, the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> knew Jaehaerys better, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a> was largely dispersed. Most importantly, however, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Aegon</a> and Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena</a> had gone on a <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progress</a> following their wedding without taking a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, as Aegon had not yet been a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonrider\" title=\"Dragonrider\">dragonrider</a> at the time, and King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a> had forbidden Rhaena from bringing <a href=\"/index.php/Dreamfyre\" title=\"Dreamfyre\">Dreamfyre</a>. Jaehaerys and Alysanne intended to travel everywhere on <a href=\"/index.php/Vermithor\" title=\"Vermithor\">Vermithor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Silverwing\" title=\"Silverwing\">Silverwing</a>, which would discourage any thought of an assault and would act as an unspoken reminder to the realm of the power of the dragons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Jaehaerys also sent out seven speakers to win the smallfolk over, not with swords, but with words. The speakers travelled the realm barefoot, going from village to village, town to town. Everywhere they went, they preached the new <a href=\"/index.php/Doctrine_of_Exceptionalism\" title=\"Doctrine of Exceptionalism\">Doctrine of Exceptionalism</a>, telling all of Jaehaerys's wisdom and Alysanne's kindness. The realm did not rise up against Jaehaerys and his queen as they had against their siblings before, although according to Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> the reasons are not entirely clear. Gyldayn cites the silence of the High Septon on the matter and the wariness of the smallfolk as important reasons... but believes that, \"if words have power\", the Seven Speakers played an important role as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When challenged by smallfolk or <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a>, who quoted passages from <i>\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Seven-Pointed_Star\" title=\"The Seven-Pointed Star\">The Seven-Pointed Star</a>\"</i> which denounced <a href=\"/index.php/Incest\" title=\"Incest\">incest</a>, the speakers simply said the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryens</a> were different. They were from <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Old Valyria</a> and were not <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">common men</a>, they could ride dragons and survive <a href=\"/index.php/Disease\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Disease\">diseases</a> that would kill lesser men.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Seven_Speakers\">The Seven Speakers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Speakers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Seven Speakers\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Elinor_Costayne\" title=\"Elinor Costayne\">Elinor Costayne</a></li>\n<li>Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Ysabel\" title=\"Ysabel\">Ysabel</a></li>\n<li>Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Violante\" title=\"Violante\">Violante</a></li>\n<li>Mother <a href=\"/index.php/Maris_(Mother)\" title=\"Maris (Mother)\">Maris</a></li>\n<li>Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Baldrick\" title=\"Baldrick\">Baldrick</a></li>\n<li>Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Rollo\" title=\"Rollo\">Rollo</a></li>\n<li>Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Alfyn_(Septon)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alfyn (Septon)\">Alfyn</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_from_the_Seven_Speakers\">Quotes from the Seven Speakers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Speakers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes from the Seven Speakers\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>One god made us all, <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrians</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>, but he did not make us all alike.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Alfyn_(septon)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alfyn (septon)\">Alfyn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Hedge knight</b>: Aye, and if I want to fuck my sister too, do I have your leave?<br />\n<b>Baldrick</b>: Go to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> and claim a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>. If you can do that, ser, I will marry you and your sister myself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Baldrick\" title=\"Baldrick\">Baldrick</a> to a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Speakers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Time of Testing - The Realm Remade.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403231544\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.047 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.068 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 633/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8861/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2973/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1629/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2505/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,